snippet.title: The Ranch of Rivershine - Announcement Trailer - New Horse Game!!
snippet.description:
Wishlist The Ranch of Rivershine on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1559600/The_Ranch_of_Rivershine/

Saddle up and build your own horse ranch! Raise foals, care for your horses and train them as you explore the western wilderness! Participate in cross country competitions and become your town's champion. Befriend the villagers who'll help you on your adventure at the Ranch of Rivershine!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/EloiseGameDev​
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/eloisegamedev
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/eloisegamedev/

Music composed by Matthew Harnage! 
Website: https://www.matthewharnage.com/
